      "created_time": "2025-05-17T16:41:00.000Z",
      "last_edited_time": "2025-05-17T16:41:00.000Z",
      "has_children": false,
      "text": "As someone living with HIV, I've faced numerous challenges and misconceptions. Through my advocacy, I aim to educate and support others in the community. Here are some key points I cover in my speeches: the importance of early testing, fighting stigma, and embracing treatment and support systems."
